PrecisEnactment of the DAKOTA TIPI BAND COUNCIL METHOD OF ELECTION REGULATIONS by giving effect to subsection 74(1) of the Act so that the Chief and Councillors of the DAKOTA TIPI BAND shall be elected by a majority of the votes of the electors of the Band.
